["O"]="You have been ordered to slay Vile Priestess Hexx and 5 Vilebranch Aman'zasi Guards. See Primal Torntusk at Revantusk Village in the Hinterlands once this task is complete.\n\nVile Priestess Hexx and the Aman'zasi Guards can be found atop Jintha'alor in the Hinterlands.",
